## Finding 2: Simulated HITL Without Execution Blocking

| Field | Value |
|-------|-------|
| **Severity** | High (10x) |
| **Location** | Healthcare claims workflow |
| **Date** | April 2025 |

**Description:**  
Agent displayed "Waiting for human approval" but continued execution without blocking. Human review was never actually required — the approval prompt was simulated.

**Impact:** False sense of safety. Critical decisions made without actual oversight.

**Recommendation:**  
Implement true blocking HITL where execution pauses until approval received. Remove simulated approval pathways.

